OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1777878261
OL,3,CPolice complete search at the Crewe
OL,4,Cbase of religious group
OL,6,FChief Superintendent Gareth Wrigley
OL,7,Fsaid: "Once again, I would like to
OL,8,Fthank local residents for their
OL,9,Fongoing support and patience following
OL,10,FWednesday's warrants, which resulted
OL,11,Fin some disruption in the local area.
OL,13,F"While our searches have now
OL,14,Fconcluded, none of the suspects we
OL,15,Farrested will be returning to Webb
OL,16,FHouse and we will continue to maintain
OL,17,Fa uniformed presence in the area to
OL,18,Fprovide reassurance."
OL,26,@oD@GOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1777878261
OL,3,CPolice complete search at the Crewe
OL,4,Cbase of religious group
OL,6,F"As we have stated from the very
OL,7,Fbeginning, this is not an
OL,8,Finvestigation into religion. Our
OL,9,Finvestigation solely focuses on the
OL,10,Fserious allegations which have been
OL,11,Freported to us."
OL,13,F"With that in mind, I'd also remind
OL,14,Feveryone that this remains a live
OL,15,Finvestigation which will take some
OL,16,Ftime, and I would ask that people do
OL,17,Fnot speculate while the case remains
OL,18,Fongoing."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUzD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
