FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1777878261
OL,3,CPolice complete search at the Crewe
OL,4,Cbase of religious group
OL,6,FThe group's leader and four others
OL,7,Farrested were made subjects of civil
OL,8,Forders to restrict their activities.
OL,10,FAccording to police, civil orders were
OL,11,Fgranted in relation to the group's
OL,12,FAmerican founder Abdullah Hashem, 42,
OL,13,Fas well as British national Ali
OL,14,FMuhammad, 35; Veronica Carla Esponda,
OL,15,F44, an Italian national; Eyad
OL,16,FElkhouly, 44, who is German, and Kevin
OL,17,FOmar Rodriguez-Ponce, 30, of Mexican
OL,18,Fnationality.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1777878261
OL,3,CPolice complete search at the Crewe
OL,4,Cbase of religious group
OL,6,FThe orders include restrictions which
OL,7,Fprevent the individuals from entering
OL,8,FCrewe, contacting the victim in the
OL,9,Fcase and having unsupervised contact
OL,10,Fwith children without the consent of
OL,11,Ftheir parents and approval from social
OL,12,Fservices.
OL,14,FThey also had to surrender their
OL,15,Fpassports and other travel documents
OL,16,Fwithin 24 hours of the order being
OL,17,Fmade.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
