OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1777878261
OL,3,CPolice complete search at the Crewe
OL,4,Cbase of religious group
OL,6,FOn Wednesday April 29, police raided
OL,7,Fproperties in Nantwich Road and Badger
OL,8,FAvenue, Crewe, as well as the
OL,9,Fcommunity's base, where 150 people are
OL,10,Fbelieved to have been living.
OL,12,FTwenty-five people were charged with
OL,13,Fpublic order offences alleged to have
OL,14,Ftaken place while those warrants were
OL,15,Fbeing carried out.
OL,17,FThey are due to appear before
OL,18,Fmagistrates next month.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
